{"tid":120750,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[花心] 我嗰兩個女朋友真係唔話得 所以我送咗份小禮物","createTime":"2017-02-14T16:04:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-14T16:18:03.000Z","uid":30859,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fcf437227869ff3dc279f3df6b89ebcb6b935544","tid":120750,"uid":30859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T16:04:01.000Z","msg":"我唔靚仔 又唔有錢<br />\n佢地兩個都無嫌棄我<br />\n佢地兩個互相知道大家既存在<br />\n佢地唔單止唔介意 仲相處得好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n無倫係日常生活 定係性事洞房 <br />\n佢地都係我嘅好幫手<br />\n口渴之時 一個會幫我拎住隻杯 另一個會幫我倒水入去 然後一齊餵我飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n行房之時 一個會係咁上下抽搐我巨龍 一個會濕潤我龜頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我真係好愛佢地 無咗任個一個都唔得<br />\n<br />\n我發覺平時都無好好咁對佢地<br />\n所以今日情人節買咗兩支凡士林hand cream 一人一支<br />\n我無用 禮物都唔貴重<br />\n但佢地一d都唔介意<br />\n依d女朋友邊度搵?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後我想講<br />\n雖然我好花心<br />\n但係我好愛我既嘅女朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df39e93b7b7ffb823c35e00dae43cf1d657ba795","tid":120750,"uid":18638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T16:07:39.000Z","msg":"知你雙手重要啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe4e15b1724b22744ea05c66559cad65475df0ba","tid":120750,"uid":37800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T16:09:27.000Z","msg":"究竟要有幾毒幾悶先可以打到呢篇又唔好笑又on9既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1673939d3031098c61037125afe0020aa8406e2b","tid":120750,"uid":22820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T16:12:51.000Z","msg":"幽默感呢家野..."},{"pid":"358b508812448623ffeb9c7f5a409fca15330654","tid":120750,"uid":11970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T16:18:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/asse